<div id=<%= "\"#{reset.id}_poke\"".html_safe %> hidden='hidden'><% mobile = Mobile.find(reset.mobile_id) %><font color=yellow>poke <%= mobile.keywords.slice(/\w+/) %></font>

<font color=silver>You poke <%= mobile.sdesc %> in the ribs.

<%= mobile.sdesc.humanize %> says 'Hello, let me tell you about myself'.

<%= mobile.sdesc.humanize %> says 'I'm level <%= mobile.level %>, and my alignment is <%= mobile.alignment %>'.
<%= mobile.sdesc.humanize %> says '<% if mobile.act_flags <= 1 %>I have no act flags<% else %>My act flags are <%= mobile.act_flags_list %><% end %>'.
<%= mobile.sdesc.humanize %> says '<% if mobile.affect_flags == 0 %>I have no affect flags<% else %>My affect flags are <%= mobile.affect_flags_list %>(-TDB-)<% end %>'.
<%= mobile.sdesc.humanize %> says 'I'm <%= mobile.animal? ? '' : 'not ' %>an animal, and I can<%= mobile.no_wear_eq? ? 'not' : '' %> wear equipment'.
<%= mobile.sdesc.humanize %> says (in <%= mobile.language_word %>) 'My known languages include <%= mobile.languages_list %>'.

></font></div>